        "subject": "=File Attached to Task: {{$json.task_title}}",
        "html": "=<p>Dear {{$json.task_owner_firstname}} {{$json.task_owner_lastname}},</p>\n\n<p>A file has been added to the task <b>{{$json.task_title}}</b>.</p>\n\n<p><b>Attachment Details</b><br>\n* Task Title: {{$json.task_title}}<br>\n* File Name: {{$json.file_name}}<br>\n* Uploaded On: {{$json.file_added_at}}</p>\n\n<p>Please review the attached document as part of task execution.</p>\n\n<p>Regards,<br>\n<b>Document & Task Management System</b></p>",
